        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\nconst articles = $('NEWS API').first().json.articles;\nconst text = articles.map(a => a.title + ': ' + a.description).join('\\n');\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    groq_body: JSON.stringify({\n      model: \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n      messages: [{\n        role: \"user\",\n        content: \"Summarize these news headlines into a clean daily digest. For each write 2 sentences:\\n\\n\" + text\n      }]\n    })\n  }\n}];"
